327
00:14:56,240 --> 00:14:57,530
working conscientiously.

328
00:14:58,790 --> 00:15:00,100
Are there scammers in the industry?

329
00:15:00,440 --> 00:15:01,300
Of course.

330
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:03,100
Then again,

331
00:15:03,750 --> 00:15:05,060
