335
00:15:10,510 --> 00:15:11,180
That's not good.

336
00:15:11,390 --> 00:15:11,890
Right?

337
00:15:15,440 --> 00:15:15,940
Makes sense.

338
00:15:17,320 --> 00:15:19,180
Then I take back what I said.

339
00:15:21,120 --> 00:15:21,700
Well,

340
00:15:23,270 --> 00:15:24,180
insurance agents,

341
00:15:25,120 --> 00:15:26,010
most of them

342
00:15:27,360 --> 00:15:28,220
aren't actually scammers.

343
00:15:29,240 --> 00:15:29,850
Happy now?

344
00:15:30,630 --> 00:15:31,420
So meticulous.

345
00:15:31,630 --> 00:15:33,820
