742
00:38:10,590 --> 00:38:11,460
Who's behind you?

743
00:38:13,440 --> 00:38:15,490
Background check was my assignment.

744
00:38:15,670 --> 00:38:16,570
Cut the crap.

745
00:38:18,110 --> 00:38:19,650
