746
00:38:20,110 --> 00:38:21,300
I'm just doing my job.

747
00:38:21,880 --> 00:38:22,530
Believe it or not.

748
00:38:23,840 --> 00:38:24,260
Fine.

749
00:38:24,790 --> 00:38:25,610
